These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, musical
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, helicopter
City: nizza, marseilles, miami
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, davidoff
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the german##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is between the italian and the person watching zombie movies##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the havana-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is the colombian##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Movie-Genre      | zombie    | musical   | crime           |
| Transport          | airplane       | helicopter    | snowmobile         |
| City         | marseilles    | miami  | nizza        |
| Cigar           | dannemann | havana   | davidoff      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Sport         | tennis     | water-polo | weightlifting |

