.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
City: prague, boston, london
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, motorbike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, lily
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, chaman
 1. the owner of the pony is the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to prague##2
 5. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | prague   | london    | boston         |
| Transport          | taxi    | snowmobile | motorbike          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Flower   | lily      | dahlia   | daisy    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Cigar         | siglo | aristoff  | chaman |

