.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
City: hamburg, colone, london
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, march
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, dancer, electrician
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, scooter, quad-bike
 1. the person traveling to colone is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the russian is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the writer is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the dancer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the dancer is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is between the indian and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the indian is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| City          | london      | colone      | hamburg      |
| Birthday         | february   | march | january |
| Job   | writer | dancer    | electrician          |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | folk      | r&b          |
| Nationality   | indian    | egyptian  | russian      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Transport         | train  | scooter   | quad-bike     |

