.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, fishing, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, swimming
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, sports
City: hamburg, paris, prague
House: modern, townhouse, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person watching disaster movies and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is swimming##2
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk           | soy-milk      |
| Hobby         | chess       | sudoku         | fishing       |
| Sport           | rowing    | snowboarding | swimming |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | sports         | disaster      |
| City   | prague         | hamburg        | paris          |
| House   | gothic-revival   | townhouse       | modern         |
| Birthday           | february       | march         | july        |

