The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, taxi
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person drinking water is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person watching crime movies##2
 6. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who likes lilac##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person eating strawberry and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the spanish is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the japanese is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
