3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
City: berlin, nizza, hannover
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, mah-jongg
 1. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the lawyer is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking almond-milk and the american##2
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is the person playing domino##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person playing domino is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Job         | manager     | freelancer     | lawyer  |
| Cigar   | swisher | montecristo  | tiparillo |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| City         | berlin    | hannover | nizza   |
| Game     | scrabble        | mah-jongg        | domino   |

