6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the fan of disco##1

