The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, lily
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, bolivar
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
