5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the person playing domino is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the fonseca-smoker##2

